{"tid":246824,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"屯元天吃喝玩樂吹水grp","createTime":"2017-05-17T10:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T17:09:36.000Z","uid":62560,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"978e6b524bfd348b5f3caeb9bce85e536b15bf49","tid":246824,"uid":62560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲返工返學咁辛苦，有冇興趣識多幾個朋友呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個grp想加住大西北既人一齊玩，咁當然你住其他地方都冇所謂，係想大家近D易攪活動多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎鐘意瘋狂吹水鐘意玩既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於係新grp，所以唔洗驚已經有小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎自組活動或即興約食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲比例一比一 最少十人成團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴禁狗公 娘娘 杜絕小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋會定期加新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地會儲埋一次過加人 麻煩留左資料既巴絲請耐心等待#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等緊你地啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/vQ4LirEmUYq1C3vB3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FvQ4LirEmUYq1C3vB3&d=T8vHa4Omq%2F1xxkbvjwgdjpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=fc2dff2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/vQ4LirEmUYq1C3vB3</a>"},{"pid":"0cc281fd5772c5d15f1b79b1a24c3e3de46a917e","tid":246824,"uid":62560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.pn